quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  22,6,un qudraton se zahir hai ke khuda hi ( Qadir mutlaq hai jo ) barhaq hai aur yeh ke woh mardon ko zindah kardaita hai. aur yeh ke woh har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai
  22,7,aur yeh ke qayamat anay wali hai. is mein kuch shak nahi. aur yeh ke khuda sab logon ko jo qabron mein hain jala uthaye ga
  22,8,aur logon mein koi aisa bhi hai jo khuda ( ki shaan ) mein baghair ilm (o danish ) ke aur baghair hadaayat ke aur baghair kitaab roshan ke jhgerta hai
  22,9,( aur taqqabur se ) gardan mourr laita ( hai ) taakay ( logon ko ) khuda ke raste se gumraah kardey. is ke liye duniya mein zillat hai. aur qayamat ke din hum usay azaab ( aatish ) sozaa ka maza chkhayin ge
  22,10,( ae sarkash ) yeh is ( kufar ) ki saza hai jo tairay hathon ne agay bheja hai aur khuda apne bundon par zulm karne wala nahi
  22,11,aur logon mein baaz aisa bhi hai jo kinare par ( khara ho kar ) khuda ki ibadat karta hai. agar is ko koi ( dunyawi ) faida puhanche to is ke sabab mutmaen hojaye aur agar koi aafat parre to munh ke bil lout jaye ( yani phir kafir hojaye ) is ne duniya mein bhi nuqsaan uthaya aur akhirat mein bhi. yahi to nuqsaan Sarih hai
  22,12,yeh khuda ke siwa aisi cheez ko pukaarta hai jo nah usay nuqsaan p_hnchaye aur nah faida day sakay. yahi to parlay darjay ki gumraahi hai
  22,13,aisay shakhs ko pukaarta hai jis ka nuqsaan faida se ziyada qareeb hai. aisa dost bura bhi aur aisa hum sohbat bhi bura
  22,14,jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay khuda un ko bahishtoon mein daakhil kere ga jin ke neechay nehrain chal rahen hain. kuch shak nahi ke khuda jo chahta hai karta hai
  22,15,jo shakhs yeh gumaan karta hai ke khuda is ko duniya aur akhirat mein madad nahi day ga to is ko chahiye ke oopar ki taraf ( yani apne ghar ki chhat mein ) aik rassi bandhay phir ( is se apna ) gala ghoont le. phir dekhe ke aaya yeh tadbeer is ke ghusse ko daur kardeti hai
